edu.stanford.math.plex

Class MappedBufferData

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.math.plex.PointData
      • edu.stanford.math.plex.PointData.NSpace
        • edu.stanford.math.plex.MappedBufferData

  • public class MappedBufferData
extends PointData.NSpace
    The MappedBufferData class is another very simple implementation of NSpace. Intended for larger, but still mappable, data sets.
